uiting-main.png 2x"> <img data-src="https://img2.storyblok.com/328x0/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/1074x500/01910192ae/e-recruiting-main.png" src="https://img2.storyblok.com/328x0/filters:format(png):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/1074x500/01910192ae/e-recruiting-main.png" class="lazy w-full h-full object-cover"></picture> <!----> <!----></div> <div class="h-[24px] md:h-[60px]"></div> <div class="w-full px-[8px] md:px-[60px] lg:px-[120px]"><div class="w-full flex items-center"><!----> <div class="ml-auto flex items-center space-x-[16px]"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https://flair.hr/de/blog/e-recruiting" class="block"><img src="/_nuxt/b2b5bc69ad0b1a07ba69512ac50df67b.svg" alt class="w-[16px] max-h-[16px] md:w-[20px] md:max-h-[20px]"></a> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://flair.hr/de/blog/e-recruiting" class="block"><img src="/_nuxt/6581a51d89f37db24453c9b5d7366af5.svg" alt class="w-[16px] max-h-[16px] md:w-[20px] md:max-h-[20px]"></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=https://flair.hr/de/blog/e-recruiting" class="block"><img src="/_nuxt/c567f1e20db8e81daa250c4215234084.svg" alt class="w-[16px] max-h-[16px] md:w-[20px] md:max-h-[20px]"></a> <button x-data="copyUrlToClipboard" x-on:click="copyUrlToClipboard()" class="block"><img src="/_nuxt/aef14a27e5a623a295ef556d575e7d15.svg" alt class="w-[16px] max-h-[16px] md:w-[20px] md:max-h-[20px]"></button></div></div> <div class="h-[24px] md:h-[60px]"></div> <div class="blog-markdown mx-auto max-w-screen-md prose prose-hr:h-[8px] prose-hr:m-0 prose-hr:border-none prose-headings:my-0 prose-headings:font-700 prose-headings:text-charcoal prose-h1:mb-[32px] prose-h1:mt-[48px] prose-h1:text-[34px] prose-h1:leading-[40px] prose-h1:tracking-[0.25px] md:prose-h1:text-[48px] md:prose-h1:leading-[56px] md:prose-h1:tracking-[0px] lg:prose-h1:text-[60px] lg:prose-h1:leading-[72px] prose-h2:text-[24px] prose-h2:leading-[32px] prose-h2:tracking-[0px] prose-h